{"tid":2244634,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"30歲男子太古廣場高叫「光復香港 時代革命」 涉違反港區國安法被捕","createTime":"2020-10-15T15:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T11:24:28.000Z","uid":21470,"like":14,"dislike":331,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"863f5a5492aec08cd7acaf4722997ea44804b7a3","tid":2244634,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T15:32:42.000Z","msg":"30歲男子太古廣場涉違反港區國安法被捕<br />\n<br />\n警方拘捕一名30歲男子，涉嫌違反港區國安法。有市民響應網上號召晚上到金鐘太古廣場，悼念去年6月15日在廣場外墮下死亡的男子梁凌杰，其間一名姓馬男子高叫「光復香港，時代革命」口號，警方指他涉嫌作出煽動或教唆他人分裂國家的行為，違反港區國安法，將他拘捕。 <br />\n<br />\n警方表示，自港區國安法7月生效以來，共有28人，包括22男6女，涉嫌違反危害國家安全的行為及活動被捕。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2361800\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2361800&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugzoCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=b7b81f64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2361800</a>"},{"pid":"5d21aa7fd47ab3ce39a1b1afc2f1dafb5a73ebd8","tid":2244634,"uid":47492,"like":14,"dislike":89,"score":-75,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T15:35:35.000Z","msg":"on9?"},{"pid":"bb731811dba377662ea42e8453c1854cb3ab4b3d","tid":2244634,"uid":47492,"like":4,"dislike":35,"score":-31,"quote":{"pid":"5d21aa7fd47ab3ce39a1b1afc2f1dafb5a73ebd8","tid":2244634,"uid":47492,"like":14,"dislike":89,"score":-75,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T15:35:35.000Z","msg":"on9?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T15:36:24.000Z","msg":"戴定頭盔 我係過黑警on9"},{"pid":"6e16ea5541ef99d4f2d6701c6091023900fa641b","tid":2244634,"uid":251732,"like":6,"dislike":16,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"5d21aa7fd47ab3ce39a1b1afc2f1dafb5a73ebd8","tid":2244634,"uid":47492,"like":14,"dislike":89,"score":-75,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T15:35:35.000Z","msg":"on9?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T15:36:32.000Z","msg":"你先至戇鳩"},{"pid":"22c1d927a4710986151f4f07850d36fb8396903c","tid":2244634,"uid":47492,"like":103,"dislike":6,"score":97,"quote":{"pid":"bb731811dba377662ea42e8453c1854cb3ab4