634,"uid":17103,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T23:26:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/文字獄\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97%E7%8D%84&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugzoCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=364038c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/文字獄</a><br />\n<br />\n文字獄，是中國專制統治者對文人的一種政治迫害，《漢語大詞典》定義為「舊時謂統治者為迫害知識份子，故意從其著作中摘取字句，羅織成罪」，羅竹風主編《漢語大詞典》，香港：三聯出版社；上海：漢語大詞典出版社，1988，6冊1518頁 由明太祖時期發展至今，較大規模的文字獄甚至可以牽連千、萬人受害。清人龔自珍詩云：「避席畏聞文字獄，著書只為稻粱謀。」[1]楊鳳城等認為文字獄是「文化現象」[2]。<br />\n<br />\n《中國大百科全書》則定義為「明清時因文字犯禁或藉文字羅織罪名清除異己而設置的刑獄。」[3]"},{"pid":"415eb723714c68b54a287196939471a9a0e44565","tid":2244634,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T23:26:34.000Z","msg":"改名叫公廁法啦"},{"pid":"b7b448cbb1c23464714ad5a6f390290e390d56a5","tid":2244634,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T23:27:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70816f31a42cda5fe7e32f786249d96a6459e035","tid":2244634,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T23:28:05.000Z","msg":"原黎講句口號香港就可以獨立建國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc2091f3b57b9d52e7a7a16c07d0d133b69c10b","tid":2244634,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T23:32:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">文字獄</span></strong>"},{"pid":"a8caae3f4fe67b345e80b3a26a6328315ce83c50","tid":2244634,"uid":88743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T23:34:41.000Z","msg":"8隻字就可以分裂國家<br />\n咁個國家而家咪四分五裂"},{"pid":"6fb00a37cd6ff0d27c8f01602