字獄，著書只為稻粱謀。」[1]楊鳳城等認為文字獄是「文化現象」[2]。<br />\n<br />\n《中國大百科全書》則定義為「明清時因文字犯禁或藉文字羅織罪名清除異己而設置的刑獄。」[3]"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T00:58:13.000Z","msg":"三聯出版社認證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f552bd93a0e5355257e4bffdf4a80b7a57d9b33b","tid":2244634,"uid":341865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8162b7c318a36dee410c5cd7034a860ffaac3791","tid":2244634,"uid":37458,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T23:22:41.000Z","msg":"呢個帖連8個字都唔敢打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲話學人叫口號碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T01:00:46.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">香港獨立 唯一出路</span>"},{"pid":"7ac0a4dcf79619c3b9c9369bba0886b7fc7128aa","tid":2244634,"uid":8091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T01:02:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ef78d9b8d26e03bd7d19121bfd73dc861d7c615","tid":2244634,"uid":155371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T01:06:49.000Z","msg":"真係荒謬"},{"pid":"1dc8e0a3aca4d3b18ae279b86d325000bb5e26ae","tid":2244634,"uid":14921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T01:36:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8f89fad32be44b3168463a03b07bad64f78cbbf5","tid":2244634,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T01:36:46.000Z","msg":"幾時拉白卡lunch"},{"pid":"f7eade8bb20c76d7c37f468668184b56aeaa59ea","tid":2244634,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f89fad32be44b3168463a03b07bad64f78cbbf5","tid":2244634,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T01:36:46.000Z","msg":"幾時拉白卡lunch"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T01:38:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RZUPqVH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRZUPqVH.png&h=e34e1d9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢仲要喺度加把口<img src=\"/assets/fa